A little fucked in the head

I came from hell with a curse

So I fucked her in church
Don’t you know
 
They say you’re not safe here if I stay
With a knife that sharp no way
 
No I leave them broken hearted
Oh no look at the mess we started
Oh no I leave the broken hearts this way
What you say
You want to play
 
Yeah don’t be fooled
I’m only letting you down
They pursued me on foot
But I hid in the crowd
Like a ghost
 
The seats of my car
Are filled with cigarette burns
I got a fire in my eye
A little blood on my shirt
Let’s hit the road
 
I know there’s a special place in hell
That my friends and I know well
There’s a perfect place to go
When it’s time to lose control
 
Nightmare daydream
You can’t save me

snippet.title: Diddy - Gotta Move On (ft. Bryson Tiller, Yung Miami, Ashanti) [Queens Remix]
snippet.description:
THE OFFICIAL VIDEO FOR GOTTA MOVE ON (QUEENS MIX) FT YUNG MIAMI AND ASHANTI

STREAM NOW : https://Diddy.lnk.to/GMOTheRemixes

LOVE RECORDS
SONG: “Gotta Move On” Remix
SONG ARTIST: Diddy, Yung Miami, Ashanti, Ron Browz

DIRECTOR: KID ART 

CREATIVE DIRECTOR: 
LAURIEANNE GIBSON

COMBS GLOBAL MANAGEMENT:  
FRANK SANTELLA / KRISTINA KHORRAM 

SALXCO MANAGEMENT : WASSIM "SAL" SLAIBY / ALAN ZADEH / DINA SHIN WASSIM

LABEL: 
LOVE RECORDS / MOTOWN  

LYRICS

Diddy:

I can feel it, love is in the air tonight, Move on
Woo, come on
And we’ve been waiting for this moment all our lives 
Move on, (Let’s Go) Move on

(We off the grid, This is the remix)

Aye Bring some DeLeón in here 
This is the remix
Aye yo turn it up, Keep on Moving

Get to the bag, yeah where that money at 
Get to the bag, yo where that money at 
Get to the bag, yeah where that money at 
Get to the bag, yeah where that money at 
Lets go

Bryson (Chorus):

She don’t want my love, I guess I gotta move on.
Yeah oh yea oh yea (Love Records)
Aye yo I like the way this sounds, stay in the frequency
She don’t want my love, I guess I gotta move on.
(And ladies report to the dance floor, report to the dance floor) 
The frequency is here
Aye yo, Caresha talk to ‘em

Yung Miami (verse):

Step 1, I can’t stress me a nigga
40 point necklace I can buy me a nigga
Deleon sipper, but my new nigga richer
He hit like his tequila, I can feel it in my liver
He ain’t moving on, he ain’t had enough of me (nah)
Half a mill on a shopping spree it ain’t enough of me
Ex nigga think I’m trippin, hot tub on the Yacht only time I’m trippin 
Concierge and a butler is how I’m living
We just went missing
Dior, Christian, everything expensive
He on my body real bad
Too fly bitch I ain’t never jet lag
Hop on his Pj, his other hoes mad 
Caresha please, he love it when I brag.

Diddy:

Get in your bag, stay in your bag (Aye yo this is the remix) 
Aye yo Ashanti..Talk to ‘em

Ashanti (Verse):

You know I tried to warn you baby
If I put this on you, it drive you crazy
Yeah I was loyal, why would you betray me
All you tried to do was fuck me and play me 
And it gets so frustrating yeah
You be playing all these games and I ain’t got time
You be out here like these niggas ain’t crazy about mine 
Like I can’t make a call and have them pull up on site 
You thought that you could have her on the weekend
Now you mad because I told you I was leaving

Nigga I’m gone nigga I’m done nigga move on,
I’m finished with it, She can have your little dick
It’s giving obsessed its giving u stress
It’s giving you press, it’s giving this nigga missing the best 
But it’s been 20 years, nigga please say less
We can see all your tears while you beating on your chest 
Said I Got a new man, you gotta move on yea

I got a new agenda with someone you probably know 
And you know I ain’t wrong, Yea I had to move on 
Yea yeah yea yeah

Bryson (Chorus):

Yeah she, If she don’t want my love, I’m guessing I gotta move on. 
I guess I guess I guess
Came on too strong I guess
If she don’t want my love, I guess I gotta move on. I guess
Don’t wanna waste your time, I guess I gotta move on. (The frequency is back) 
If she don’t want my love, I guess I gotta move on. I guess

Somebody Shine a light on em’
Shine a light on em’
Somebody Shine a light on em’ (get in your bag stay in your bag) 
Shine a light on em’ (get in your bag stay in your bag)
We going up we going live
Can’t stop won’t stop told y’all See me pull up no problem
I can never ever be no one option Pull up on me but no blogs 
Now you wanna say you wan talk
Now you wanna say you wan talk
Now you wanna say you wan
Get in your bag, stay in your bag
Get in your bag, stay in your bag
Get in your bag, stay in your bag
Get in your bag, stay in your bag
Love Records
